<Justin Anderson/> twists his ankle as he attempts to chase down <Courtney Lee/> and is clearly in pain as he limps off the court. (0:34)

<Anderson/> out for game with sprained right ankle (0:34)

Philadelphia swingman <Justin Anderson/> sprained his right ankle in the Sixers' game against the New York Knicks on Monday night and will not return.

X-rays were negative, the team said.

<Anderson/> is averaging 6.2 points in 14.4 minutes a game for the Sixers.